---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — Fisch Values App"
  description="Terms of Service for the Fisch Values mobile application."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="main">
    <div class="page-wrap">
      <h1 class="page-title">Terms of Service — Fisch Values App</h1>

      <div class="content">
        <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> March 2026</p>

        <p>
          By downloading, installing, or using <strong>Fisch Values</strong> ("the App"), you agree to be bound by these
          Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, do not use the App.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Disclaimer — Fan-Made Application</h2>
        <p>
          Fisch Values is a fan-made application and is <strong>NOT</strong> affiliated with, endorsed by, sponsored by, or
          connected to Roblox Corporation or the developers of Fisch in any way. All game content,
          including but not limited to item names, images, and game mechanics, are the property of their
          respective owners. This app is an independent tool created to assist players with trading
          decisions and game information.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Eligibility</h2>
        <p>
          You must be at least 13 years of age to use this App. By using the App, you represent and
          warrant that you are at least 13 years old. If you are under 18, you represent that you have
          your parent or guardian's permission to use the App.
        </p>

        <h2>3. User Accounts</h2>
        <p>To access certain features, you may need to create an account. You are responsible for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials</li>
          <li>All activities that occur under your account</li>
          <li>Notifying us immediately of any unauthorized use</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these Terms.</p>

        <h2>4. Trading Values Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          The trade values, item prices, and market data provided in this App are estimates based on
          community data and are for <strong>informational purposes only</strong>. We do not guarantee the accuracy,
          completeness, or timeliness of any values displayed. Trading decisions are made at your own
          risk. We are not responsible for any losses incurred from trades based on information provided
          by this App.
        </p>

        <h2>5. User Conduct</h2>
        <p>You agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use the App for any illegal purpose</li>
          <li>Post false, misleading, or fraudulent trade listings</li>
          <li>Harass, abuse, or harm other users</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to the App or its systems</li>
          <li>Use automated scripts, bots, or scrapers on the App</li>
          <li>Impersonate another person or entity</li>
          <li>Interfere with or disrupt the App's functionality</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          The App's design, code, and original content are owned by Codigos Gratis. Game-related content
          (item names, images, descriptions) belong to their respective rights holders and are used under
          fair use for informational purposes. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative
          works from the App without our written permission.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          THE APP IS PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR
          IMPLIED. TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, CODIGOS GRATIS SHALL NOT BE LIABLE
          FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, INCLUDING BUT NOT
          LIMITED TO LOSS OF PROFITS, DATA, OR GOODWILL, ARISING FROM YOUR USE OF THE APP.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Indemnification</h2>
        <p>
          You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Codigos Gratis, its officers, directors, employees, and
          agents from any claims, damages, losses, or expenses arising from your use of the App or
          violation of these Terms.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Termination</h2>
        <p>
          We may terminate or suspend your access to the App at any time, without prior notice, for any
          reason, including violation of these Terms. Upon termination, your right to use the App ceases
          immediately. You may delete your account at any time from the App Settings.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Dispute Resolution</h2>
        <p>
          Any disputes arising from these Terms or your use of the App shall be resolved through binding
          arbitration in accordance with applicable laws, rather than in court. You agree to waive your
          right to participate in a class action lawsuit or class-wide arbitration.
        </p>

        <h2>11. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be effective when posted
          in the App. Your continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated
          Terms. We encourage you to review these Terms periodically.
        </p>

        <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:info@codigos-gratis.com">info@codigos-gratis.com</a><br />
          Website: <a href="https://codigos-gratis.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">codigos-gratis.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .main {
    padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .page-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .content ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .content strong {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .content a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .content a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
</style>
